{"tid":962982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"延禧攻略明年2月將於日本播出，劇名令網友們直呼崩潰！","createTime":"2018-12-31T09:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T16:29:54.000Z","uid":25345,"like":276,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"5284bcb48969f2c336fedc36afec4548587aa7a7","tid":962982,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181229/427c69dd43a54c7281d8d5919f8150b1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20181229%2F427c69dd43a54c7281d8d5919f8150b1.jpeg&h=c0692e37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n引起全球宮鬥劇熱潮的《延禧攻略》，播放版權熱賣90個國家，更榮登Google全球2018年搜尋量最高的電視劇，而日本版也即將在明年2月播出了！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消息指出，日版《延禧攻略》將於2019年2月18日放送，網上也放出了宣傳海報，風格強烈的<br />\n<br />\n最令人崩潰的是，日本竟將《延禧攻略》的劇名改為《纓絡，紫禁城燃燒的逆襲王妃》，令人哭笑不得。網友笑稱，不如乾脆叫《帝國猛妃&mdash;魏瓔珞醬》或是《瓔珞&middot;孝儀純皇后升職記》（番外篇）算了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不只日本，美國有權威媒體近期也將《延禧攻略》評為2018年最佳海外劇集。前陣子網路上還流傳著一名老外透過翻譯器觀看《延禧攻略》的影片，吸引網友瘋狂點閱與轉PO。"},{"pid":"54e583d0b074dbf6c8b5aeb316c991f15d5d9dca","tid":962982,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29490b5d072f1c199040ce4d024fc829b17fa169","tid":962982,"uid":30067,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:24:47.000Z","msg":"想睇日配音<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78fbeb8cb6465f944c1504b29614980f583c7acc","tid":962982,"uid":94828,"like":652,"dislike":2,"score":650,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"封面成套av咁"},{"pid":"0c8fbf8159ca2fd3d901c4175abb3380cc9791e4","tid":962982,"uid":213441,"like":219,"dislike":3,"score":216,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:27:33.000Z","msg":"紫禁宮<code>&amp;</code>&amp;淫=&times;相奸xxyy 夫目前犯"},{"pid":"c97a0a98f0250b94b889e897a25f395c